publicwhip.minor-heading: Association of Chief Police Officers: Finance

ques.p: To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department what (a) budgetary support and (b) other funding her Department has given to the Association of Chief Police Officers in the last 12 months.

reply.p: I refer the hon. Member to the answer I gave the hon. Member for Southend, West (Mr. Amess) on 20 April 2009, Official Report, column 147W.
